snippet: Louis Oosthuizen made a long birdie putt at the final green to take a one-shot lead after the second round of the Volvo Champions in Durban, South Africa.
abstract: Louis Oosthuizen takes second-round lead at Volvo Champions golf tournament in Durban, South Africa.
lead_paragraph: Louis Oosthuizen made a long birdie putt at the final green to take a one-shot lead after the second round of the Volvo Champions in Durban, South Africa.

headline.main: Oosthuizen Leads Volvo by a Shot
